Modifications (Apache-2.0 section 4(b): notice of changes)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This fork has been substantially modified relative to the upstream project.
Significant changes include:

  • Inline mechanical checking re-implemented on Automattic Harper (Rust →
    WebAssembly) instead of the original inline engine.
  • Added a local n-gram noisy-channel context re-ranker for spelling
    candidate disambiguation, with a bundled pruned frequency model.
  • Correction flow re-architected to whole-sentence LLM rewrite
    (/correct, /rephrase) rather than offset-merged rule fragments.
  • Ollama memory management: configurable idle keep_alive, explicit
    /ollama-unload, and graceful unload on shutdown.
  • Added the Abacus RouteLLM provider.
  • Provider API key now AES-GCM encrypted at rest (never synced/plaintext).
  • Options/popup/highlighter UI rework, including an on-demand "Improve"
    (tone rewrite) control on the floating assistant.
  • Added a server-less inline-engine regression harness.

These changes are the work of the fork's contributors and are not endorsed
by or affiliated with the original author.

This product includes third-party software.

