-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
N-gram frequency model (inline context re-ranker)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The local context re-ranker (ngram/model.bin) is a compact, pruned table of
unigram and bigram *frequency counts* derived from the public word- and
bigram-frequency lists published by Peter Norvig:

  https://norvig.com/ngrams/count_1w.txt
  https://norvig.com/ngrams/count_2w.txt

Only aggregate statistical counts (facts, not expressive content) are used,
and they are transformed into a pruned binary log-probability model by
scripts/build-ngram-model.mjs. No source text is redistributed. The model is
regenerable with `npm run build:ngram`.
